---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Nav.astro";
---

<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<Navigation />
<Layout title="欢迎">
	<main>
		<svg
			class="astro-a"
			width="495"
			height="623"
			viewBox="0 0 495 623"
			fill="none"
			xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
			aria-hidden="true"
		>
			<path
				fill-rule="evenodd"
				clip-rule="evenodd"
				d="M167.19 364.254C83.4786 364.254 0 404.819 0 404.819C0 404.819 141.781 19.4876 142.087 18.7291C146.434 7.33701 153.027 0 162.289 0H332.441C341.703 0 348.574 7.33701 352.643 18.7291C352.92 19.5022 494.716 404.819 494.716 404.819C494.716 404.819 426.67 364.254 327.525 364.254L264.41 169.408C262.047 159.985 255.147 153.581 247.358 153.581C239.569 153.581 232.669 159.985 230.306 169.408L167.19 364.254ZM160.869 530.172C160.877 530.18 160.885 530.187 160.894 530.195L160.867 530.181C160.868 530.178 160.868 530.175 160.869 530.172ZM136.218 411.348C124.476 450.467 132.698 504.458 160.869 530.172C160.997 529.696 161.125 529.242 161.248 528.804C161.502 527.907 161.737 527.073 161.917 526.233C165.446 509.895 178.754 499.52 195.577 500.01C211.969 500.487 220.67 508.765 223.202 527.254C224.141 534.12 224.23 541.131 224.319 548.105C224.328 548.834 224.337 549.563 224.347 550.291C224.563 566.098 228.657 580.707 237.264 593.914C245.413 606.426 256.108 615.943 270.749 622.478C270.593 621.952 270.463 621.508 270.35 621.126C270.045 620.086 269.872 619.499 269.685 618.911C258.909 585.935 266.668 563.266 295.344 543.933C298.254 541.971 301.187 540.041 304.12 538.112C310.591 533.854 317.059 529.599 323.279 525.007C345.88 508.329 360.09 486.327 363.431 457.844C364.805 446.148 363.781 434.657 359.848 423.275C358.176 424.287 356.587 425.295 355.042 426.275C351.744 428.366 348.647 430.33 345.382 431.934C303.466 452.507 259.152 455.053 214.03 448.245C184.802 443.834 156.584 436.019 136.218 411.348Z"
				fill="url(#paint0_linear_1805_24383)"></path>
			<defs>
				<linearGradient
					id="paint0_linear_1805_24383"
					x1="247.358"
					y1="0"
					x2="247.358"
					y2="622.479"
					gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
				>
					<stop stop-opacity="0.9"></stop>
					<stop offset="1" stop-opacity="0.2"></stop>
				</linearGradient>
			</defs>
			<Navigation />
		</svg>
		<img
			src="https://img.ixintu.com/download/jpg/201912/f2e86f314f632e1e21ceaed65aa735a6.jpg!con"
			alt="Description of the image"
		/>
		<h1><span class="text-gradient">未来探索</span></h1>
		<p class="instructions">
			引领用户领略 <code>未来科技</code> 的魅力<br />
			预见社会发展的<strong>新趋势</strong> 以及思考人类未来的<strong
				>可能性</strong
			>。
		</p>

		<h2>
			<li><a href="/md/4">未来科技展望→</a></li>
		</h2>
		<div class="text-with-image">
			<img
				class="aa"
				src="https://img.tukuppt.com/ad_preview/00/44/51/603eef8277094.jpg!/fw/980"
				alt="未来科技"
			/><p>
				未来科技展望呈现出多元化和深度发展的趋势，涵盖了从太空探索到人工智能、从生物技术到虚拟现实等多个领域。
			</p>
		</div>
		<h2>
			<li><a href="/html/3">未来社会与生活→</a></li>
		</h2>
		<div class="text-with-image">
			<img
				class="aa"
				src="https://img.zcool.cn/community/0107bb5b18bbcaa801202e60cd2b9e.jpg?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,m_lfit,w_1280,limit_1/sharpen,100"
				alt="未来生活"
			/><p>
				未来社会与生活将呈现出智能化、数字化、可持续化、个性化、全球化等趋势。这些变化将为我们带来更加便捷、高效、舒适和美好的生活方式，同时也需要我们不断适应和学习新的知识和技能。
			</p>
		</div>
		<h2>
			<li><a href="/html/4">未来愿景与思考→</a></li>
		</h2>
		<div class="text-with-image">
			<img
				class="aa"
				src="https://ts1.cn.mm.bing.net/th/id/R-C.b2f5350b2ece067042c1fbefb5ecdfc1?rik=8efYzSKaU9QocQ&riu=http%3a%2f%2fimg.ugainian.com%2f267%2f5dd63f5d9931a.jpeg&ehk=1n4j5lN%2bFmu5%2bNzypG4e5h%2boA347FJzMPDVUwJ%2bZe0Q%3d&risl=&pid=ImgRaw&r=0"
				alt="未来"
			/><p>
				未来充满了挑战和机遇。我们需要保持开放的心态和创新的精神，积极应对未来的挑战并抓住机遇。同时，我们也需要关注社会公正和人类福祉，确保科技的发展能够惠及每一个人。
			</p>
		</div>
	</main>

	<style>
		main {
			margin: auto;
			padding: 1rem;
			width: 800px;
			max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
			color: white;
			font-size: 20px;
			line-height: 1.6;
		}
		.astro-a {
			position: absolute;
			top: -32px;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translatex(-50%);
			width: 220px;
			height: auto;
			z-index: -1;
		}
		h1 {
			font-size: 4rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			line-height: 1;
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: 1em;
		}
		h2 {
			color: black;
			font-family: 35xp;
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
			gap: 1rem;
			padding: 0;
			font-style: 楷体;
		}
		.text-gradient {
			background-image: linear-gradient(
				rgba(255, 201, 5, 0.66),
				rgba(36, 35, 14, 0.33)
			);
			-webkit-background-clip: text;
			-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			background-size: 400%;
			background-position: 0%;
			font-size: 40px;
			font-family: 楷体, sans-serif;
		}
		.instructions {
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
			border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
			background: linear-gradient(
				rgba(224, 196, 94, 0.66),
				rgba(250, 245, 102, 0.33)
			);
			padding: 1.5rem;
			border-radius: 8px;
			color: black;
			font-family: 宋体;
		}
		.instructions code {
			font-size: 1em;
			font-weight: bold;
			background: linear-gradient(
				rgba(247, 245, 237, 0.66),
				rgba(244, 243, 193, 0.33)
			);
			border-radius: 4px;
			padding: 0.3em 0.4em;
			color: #ba7a03;
		}
		.instructions strong {
			color: #ba7a03;
		}
		p {
			color: black;
		}
		.banner img {
			max-width: 100%;
			height: auto;
		}
		.text-with-image {
			display: flex;
			align-items: flex-start;
		}
		.text-with-image img {
			margin-right: 10px;
			max-width: 50%;
			height: auto;
		}
		a {
			text-decoration: none;
			color: #ba7a03;
		}
		img {
			width: 100%;
			height: 300px;
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
